				<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/𪺠"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2AEA0;</span></a><a href="/whv/𥡥"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x25865;</span></a><a href="/whv/𥎋"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2538B;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡠴"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x21834;</span></a><a href="/whv/聰"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8070;</span></a><a href="/whv/牕"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7255;</span></a><a href="/whv/熜"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x719C;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
